          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mingyizhao/" class=" " title="洛奇">洛奇</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11811465">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">United States is the result of communication, compromise and agreement of all the people in that land. Therefore, since the beginning, states hold far more power than the federal government.

This character actually is one of the keys to become the most successful country in this world. Because such a system leads to the competition and selection of laws, institutions, ethics, economics, etc. Ba...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-03-12 23:14</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                United States is the result of communication, compromise and agreement of all the people in that land. Therefore, since the beginning, states hold far more power than the federal government.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>This character actually is one of the keys to become the most successful country in this world. Because such a system leads to the competition and selection of laws, institutions, ethics, economics, etc. Bad ones are sift out, leaving what is really good.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Other countries, especially those who adopted totalitarian, are based on the will of the leader. However, human's intelligence cannot beat the nature selection. So most of these countries are moving slowly.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>In this book, we can see how a country grow. But in the history of China, we seldom find the trace of moving forward.
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







